snippet: Agnieszka Radwanska extended the best winning streak of the year to 11 matches as she rolled into the third round of the Australian Open with a 6-3, 6-3 win over Irina-Camelia Begu of Romania.
abstract: Tennis Roundup; Agnieszka Radwanska defeats Irina-Camelia Begu in second round of Australian Open; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Agnieszka Radwanska extended the best winning streak of the year to 11 matches as she rolled into the third round of the Australian Open with a 6-3, 6-3 win over Irina-Camelia Begu of Romania.

headline.main: Radwanska Remains Undefeated for the Year
